195. Memorandum of ConversationSource: National Archives, Nixon Presidential Materials, NSC Files, Box 664, Country Files, Middle East, Middle East
                            War, Memos and Miscellaneous, October 6–17, 1973. Top Secret; Sensitive;
                            Nodis. Drafted by Quandt. The
                            meeting took place in the Oval Office. Kissinger met with the Foreign Ministers at 10:15 in his
                            White House office. (Memorandum of conversation, October 17;
                            ibid.)
